            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間09日03:46，恆生科技指數上漲182.87點（或4%），暫報4751.25點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：-15.52%</li><li>近 1 月：-24.33%</li><li>近 3 月：+6.06%</li><li>近 6 月：-2.71%</li><li>今年以來：+2.24%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>環球市場概念領漲+7.82%。其中    ＦＩ二華夏納一百(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:07522:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/07522\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">07522-HK</a>)            上漲        6.67%            ;        ＦＩ二南方納指(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:07568:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/07568\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">07568-HK</a>)            上漲        6.66%            ;    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>航空、航天及國防概念領漲+6.39%。其中    中航科工(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02357:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02357\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02357-HK</a>)            上漲        8.33%            ;        航天控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00031:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00031\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00031-HK</a>)            上漲        7.46%            ;        大陸航空科技控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00232:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\